{"tid":1724611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［變通］星期五仲守乜野中大","createTime":"2019-11-15T13:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:55:15.000Z","uid":158766,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f47b513526b606b3482c66d724d6cd3de9c830e1","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"本身死守中大都係為條橋搞火車咋 好多地方都有啦 都唔好講聽日後日啲人唔駛返工黎緊兩日再硬守根本冇三罷意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有星期二一役全世界都知係前線守到狗 打起左個士氣 晏晝冇狗攻果陣黎走完全唔算係認輸 怕咩傷士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今朝個記招溝通上有嚴重失誤 早就趕走左好多人 而家裡面得返三幾十個人 同送頭有咩分別？唔係嫌去港島送頭架咩 而家得返丁咁多人係中大就唔算送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日你空城左比佢 之後嘅日子再返去咪得囉 慌佢係裡面紮營做保安咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日話乜野聚唔返人 得返30個係裡面 人都走晒啦 要講聚唔到人係今朝有人走之前講先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更何況五年前走話聚唔到人 五年後啲人咪一樣出返晒黎 場仗有排打 有必要執著一個地方嘅佔領咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁有佔領情意結 駛唔駛重新去佔過金鐘旺角銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Be Water係一種精神 唔係純粹郁個身就係be water呀 可唔可以全部手足一齊搵返運動初期嘅果種變通呀 呢樣野先係班狗同狗官最招架唔到架</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6800af670300ea00c0badd23f10ccf54a086cc2c","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fafbbd433b6921de38f655183087f393fd6d96","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f819c481388eb31d625504d27648408dd3a76543","tid":1724611,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"聽日要返工(理論上)路過<br />\n香港係有好多人禮拜六要返工架小朋友"},{"pid":"7ecdaca3ffb503c52a84e20a839db6a7972153e5","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd2ff7db324d389496cc59849ea01b5e5d38bad","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f819c481388eb31d625504d27648408dd3a76543","tid":1724611,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"聽日要返工(理論上)路過<br />\n香港係有好多人禮拜六要返工架小朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"幾多呀 夠唔夠一至五咁多？ 有冇衡量過裡面發生過咩事兼得返三十個呀 小朋友"},{"pid":"735c719e6bab70be40ec566e13fd3e523a85dc64","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6787de26c0856a6122b4706136c4290d194d63cc","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b237dca21eb5cdcb375185ba30b19d6cb4f542b","tid":1724611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":